replies.msg:
.@Besiktas in talks with @LFC about a move for Simon Mignolet. Olympiakos also have made an approach for Lazar Markovic. <br />
<br />
@LFC looking for between &pound;5m-&pound;7m for Markovic, with Standard Liege and a number of English sides keeping tabs. Much more interest in Mignolet, for whom the club will only countenance a sale,  not a loan.

